#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kalzium</command> <group><option>Options</option></group> <group "
"choice=\"opt\"><option>--molecule <replaceable>filename</replaceable></"
"option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kalzium</command> <group><option>Opcións</option></group> <group "
"choice=\"opt\"><option>--molecule <replaceable>nome-de-ficheiro</"
"replaceable></option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descrición"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; is a program which shows you the Periodic System of the Elements "
"(PSE). You can use &kalzium; to search for information about the elements or "
"to learn facts about the PSE."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; é un programa que amosa a táboa periódica dos elementos. Pode usar "
"&kalzium; para buscar información sobre os elementos ou para aprender cousas "
"sobre a táboa mesma."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; provides you with all kinds of information about the PSE. You can "
"look up lots of information about the elements and also use visualisations "
"to show them."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; fornece todo tipo de información sobre a táboa periódica. Pode "
"buscar moreas de información sobre os elementos e tamén usar visualizacións "
"para amosalos."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "This package is part of the official KDE edutainment module."
msgstr "Este paquete é parte do módulo oficial de KDE para educación."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcións"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "--molecule <replaceable>filename</replaceable>"
msgstr "--molecule <replaceable>nome-de-ficheiro</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the given molecule file in cml, xyz, ent, pdb, alc, chm, cdx, cdxml, "
"c3d1, c3d2, gpr, mdl, mol, sdf, sd, crk3d, cht, dmol, bgf, gam, inp, gamin, "
"gamout, tmol, fract, mpd, or mol2 format."
msgstr ""
"Abrir o ficheiro de molécula indicado en formato cml, xyz, ent, pdb, alc, "
"chm, cdx, cdxml, c3d1, c3d2, gpr, mdl, mol, sdf, sd, crk3d, cht, dmol, bgf, "
"gam, inp, gamin, gamout, tmol, fract, mpd, ou mol2."

